from rkwmo mnr m oosthuysen subject re a kind and loving god in article jmeritt write leviticu and the daughter of any priest if she profane herself by play the whore she profaneth her father she shall be burn with fire deuteronomy and the token of virginity be not find for the damsel then they shall bring out the damsel to the door of her father house and the man of the city shall stone her with stone that she die deuteronomy if a man be find lie with a woman marry to a husband then they shall both of them die deuteronomy if a damsel that be a virgin be betroth unto a husband and a man find her in the city and lie with her then ye shall bring them both out unto the gate of that city and ye shall stone them with stone that they die deuteronomy but if a man find a betroth damsel in the field and the man force her and lie with her then the man only that lay with her shall die if it for the sin of man none of thi kill would have be necesarry he be kind and loving but also righteou sin must be punished before jesu man have to take the sin on himself but jesu die and take it all upon him so now we also have a forgiving god if he be not kind and loving there would have be any person leave 